1. PREAMBLE: THE DOCTRINE OF PURE POWER
This software is engineered under the "Pure Power" philosophy. 
It is designed for efficiency, speed, and professional integrity. 
If you lack respect for the machine, this software is not for you.

2. CREDIT AND BRANDING REQUIREMENTS
Any distribution, in source or binary form, MUST retain the attribution 
